Lesson 11   Is this your shirt?

2
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:13,810
Listen to the tape then answer this question.

3
00:00:13,810 --> 00:00:18,970
Whose shirt is white?

4
00:00:18,970 --> 00:00:22,380
Whose shirt is that?

5
00:00:22,380 --> 00:00:26,820
Is this your shirt, Dave?

6
00:00:26,820 --> 00:00:28,660
No. Sir.

7
00:00:28,660 --> 00:00:32,430
It's not my shirt.

8
00:00:32,430 --> 00:00:35,710
This is my shirt.

9
00:00:35,710 --> 00:00:40,390
My shirt's blue.

10
00:00:40,390 --> 00:00:44,700
Is this shirt Tim's?

11
00:00:44,700 --> 00:00:47,610
Perhaps it is, sir.

12
00:00:47,610 --> 00:00:51,940
Tim's shirt's white.

13
00:00:51,940 --> 00:00:58,660
Tim!

14
00:00:58,660 --> 00:00:03,930
Yes, sir?

15
00:00:03,930 --> 00:00:53,570
Is this your shirt?

16
00:00:53,570 --> 00:01:01,370
Yes, sir.

17
00:01:01,370 --> 00:01:02,910
Here you are.

18
00:01:02,910 --> 00:01:04,920
Catch!

19
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:05,920
Thank you, sir.
